# Espada 2
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Espada 2 is a 2D vertical space shooter. This was made as an improved version of the first game, Espada.



## Copyright & License

Espada 2 is Copyright (c) 2013 Justin Jacobs

Espada 2's source code is released under the GNU GPL v3. Later versions are permitted.

The included VDS font is licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.

data/sounds/explosion.ogg is a modified version of sandyrb's 'THE CRASH.wav' (http://www.freesound.org/people/sandyrb/sounds/95078/), which was released under CC-BY 3.0.

All other artwork is by me, Justin Jacobs, and is licensed under CC-BY-SA 3.0.



## Dependencies & Building

* SDL
* SDL_ttf
* SDL_image
* SDL_mixer

To compile Espada 2, simply run `make` in the base directory.



## Controls

* Arrow keys / Joystick D-pad = Move ship
* Z / Joystick Button 0 = Fire laser / Confirm menu selection
* ESC / Joystick Button 9 = Pause the game

